        <Note_Text>Authoritative instructions for conduct or prescriptive instructions regarding a certain procedure, activity, or topic. Examples are instructions governing procedure in documentation or cataloging, for a legislative body, game, sport, or contest. For less prescriptive recommendations, use "guidelines."</Note_Text>
